---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout title="Why TORVIX - The Toronto Standard in Luxury Renovation">
  <Header />
  
  <main class="flex-grow pt-32 lg:pt-40 min-h-screen bg-[#f9f8f6]">
    
    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32">
      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center reveal">
        <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-8 tracking-tight">
          Why Choose TORVIX
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-slate-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed tracking-wide font-sans">
          In Toronto's luxury real estate market, excellence is not a subjective metric—it is an engineered reality. We distinguish ourselves through a rigid adherence to process, transparency, and architectural integrity.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 lg:py-32 border-t border-slate-200 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 lg:gap-24">
          
          <div class="reveal delay-100">
            <span class="text-xs font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4 block">01</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6 tracking-tight">Uncompromising Engineering Standards</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              We do not take shortcuts. Beneath the premium finishes lies a foundation of rigorous engineering. From load-bearing structural modifications to complex MEP (Mechanical, Electrical, Plumbing) routing, every system is designed and installed to exceed building codes. True luxury requires a flawless foundation.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal delay-200">
            <span class="text-xs font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4 block">02</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6 tracking-tight">Transparent Project Management</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              Construction should never be a black box. We operate on radical transparency. You will receive clear, detailed contracts, honest timeline projections, and proactive communication. There are no hidden fees or surprise alterations—just professional project management from day one to handover.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal delay-100">
            <span class="text-xs font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4 block">03</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6 tracking-tight">Speed Without Sacrificing Detail</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              We recognize that your time is an invaluable asset. Through advanced logistics, synchronized trades scheduling, and meticulous material procurement, we execute complex renovations rapidly. We deliver velocity without ever compromising the microscopic details that define high-end residential architecture.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal delay-200">
            <span class="text-xs font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-slate-400 mb-4 block">04</span>
            <h2 class="text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-serif text-[#1a1a1a] mb-6 tracking-tight">Toronto Market Expertise</h2>
            <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed font-sans tracking-wide">
              We understand the nuances of Toronto real estate. Whether navigating strict strata rules in a downtown high-rise or integrating modern extensions into a historic Forest Hill estate, we have the specialized expertise to maneuver through local zoning, board approvals, and urban logistical challenges seamlessly.
            </p>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="py-32 bg-[#1a1a1a] text-[#f9f8f6] text-center">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 reveal">
        <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-serif mb-8 tracking-tight">Experience the Standard.</h2>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-10 py-4 bg-transparent border border-white/30 text-white font-medium font-sans tracking-widest uppercase text-sm rounded-none hover:bg-white hover:text-[#1a1a1a] transition-all duration-500 ease-in-out">
          Discuss Your Project
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>
